txt.en: Dorri wants dull beaks. Dorri can be found standing at the west gate of Gondamon.
Wanted: Dull beaks from the hendrevail in Ered Luin. Collect them and deliver them to Dorri at Gondamon to earn favour with Thorin's Hall.
You have accepted a task to acquire dull beaks. You are to deliver them to Dorri at the western gate of Gondamon to earn favour with Thorin's Hall.
'Good riddance to these creatures...too many of them around for us to feel comfortable.\n\n'Your efforts will echo through the halls.'
'Be sure that you are not killing the weak hendrevail...they have different looking beaks.'
Wanted: Dull beaks from the hendrevail in Ered Luin.
Deliver the dull beaks to Dorri at Gondamon
Thank you for contributing your collection! Please place your items in the box to receive your award.
You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
